      "message": "Is is necessary to create the mocks each time in the @BeforeEach setUp method especially when nothing really changes? This could be simply done on the field level. Each test method is already run on a new instance.\n\nAlso the when() clause is duplicated in first test. I'd consider removing this method and doing everything in the tests.",
